ury while playing squash. “His doctors would give an update of the treatment later today-Laolu Akande, VP’s Spokesperson.” Attempts made to get more information on the matter did not yield results as the Vice President’s spokesman did not pick calls on his gsm .    Professor Yemi Osinbajo VICE President Yemi Osinbajo has been hospitalized for a surgical procedure on account of recurrent pain in the leg. This was disclosed on Twitter by Mr. Laolu Akande, the Senior Special Assistant to the President on Media and Publicity to Vice President Yemi Osinbajo.  He wrote, "VP… In "Health" By Johnbosco Agbakwuru VICE President Yemi Osinbajo on Monday rendered a helping hand to an accident victim along Abuja airport road as he ordered that the ambulance in his convoy be used to take an accident victim to hospital. An online platform had reported that Prof. Osinbajo's convoy was involved… In "News" MSMEs poised to leapfrog Nigeria into economic prosperity — Osinbajo In "Business"